                    "body": "It seems `arrow-rs` defaults to RLE for the boolean array; but that can be changed using a different encoding thru [set_encoding|https://docs.rs/parquet/latest/parquet/file/properties/struct.WriterPropertiesBuilder.html#method.set_encoding] on the Builder.\r\n\r\nOther good news, is pyarrow 10.x should (and does work, checking on master now) read the given file, thanks to ARROW-18031  being closed.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nEDIT: If this answers the question/issue, can we close this?",
